[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "九偉人図、あれには描き手の生き様が込められている。\nあれを欲するのなら、それ相応の生き様を見せてみろ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "これは……獣人限定、ベスティラ武道会の告知？\n全員一斉参加、最後まで残った者が勝利……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "優勝者にはベスティラ王が可能な範囲で\n願いを１つ叶えてくれる……これに参加しろと？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうだ。これに勝ち残り、「九偉人図」を望むがいい。\n見たところお前も腕に覚えがあるのだろう？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "欲しいものがあるのならば、\nお前の生き様で、掴み取ってみせるがいい！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……武道会に出てくれるのはすっごく助かる。\nでもあんなことがあったんだし、無理しちゃダメだよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "だいじょーぶ、アイスなんかへっちゃらだから。\nそれに、ジェロンとティム君だって出るもんね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "僕は生まれつきの獣人じゃないけど……\n皆さんのために頑張ります！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ああ、俺も全力を尽くそう。\nティムには傷一つ付けさせん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "改めてだけど、細かい決まりとかはないんだよね？\nなんでもありのガチンコ対決？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "実際に戦うのが獣人であること以外、\n特に制限はないみたいです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "武器や道具の持ち込みも問題ないようだな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "道具となると……レスナ、\nやっぱりアタシたちの出番ってことだね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん！　錬金術士として、全力でみんなを支援しよう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "本番で役立つ道具……傷薬や、力の出る携帯食料、\nあとは爆弾とか……ありったけを用意しよう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "なら、俺もアトリエに戻るべきだな。\n道具の準備が勝敗を左右しそうだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "素材も集めてこなきゃね！\n砂漠の国ならではの食材、探してみようかな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "武道会本番まで時間がない……\n急いで調合にかかろう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]